title: Swaps & Fitness for Person with Disabilities
description:
And yes...they are pretty simple.  But what a major impact these replacements can have on your well being.  Then it's caller time where JIllian answers questions on diet, fitness and overall wellness.  This week's show also takes on a topic that very few take on...fitness for person's with disabilities.
